{"tid":2056922,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"《七一立會案改控暴動》明天東區裁判法院下午2時30分提堂","createTime":"2020-06-09T04:40:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-09T14:00:24.000Z","uid":240362,"like":10,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"eb48f57d0aecdf092d9d44bd74210a4e37a320c6","tid":2056922,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T04:40:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent-hkt1-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/p960x960/102970505_1349446191892439_6275838380189566573_o.jpg?_nc_cat=105&amp;_nc_sid=8024bb&amp;_nc_ohc=XFVaLJfa19QAX8kuqiy&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-hkt1-1.xx&amp;_nc_tp=6&amp;oh=8dbd9762e3f00d4bf44c54e907b83002&amp;oe=5F02B48C\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkt1-1.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2Fp960x960%2F102970505_1349446191892439_6275838380189566573_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D105%26_nc_sid%3D8024bb%26_nc_ohc%3DXFVaLJfa19QAX8kuqiy%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-hkt1-1.xx%26_nc_tp%3D6%26oh%3D8dbd9762e3f00d4bf44c54e907b83002%26oe%3D5F02B48C&h=996bd8fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/ventuslauwh/photos/a.609574135879652/1349446188559106/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fventuslauwh%2Fphotos%2Fa.609574135879652%2F1349446188559106%2F&d=N73AYdKZ8ITSJgwUZ5%2B19vkXgXr6FxeO6pMo8RORPdo%3D&h=f51cc1fd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/ventuslauwh/photos/a.609574135879652/1349446188559106/</a><br />\n<br />\n劉頴匡 Ventus Lau<br />\n&middot; 12 mins &middot; <br />\n <br />\n《七一立會案改控暴動》<br />\n<br />\n我因涉嫌去年七月一日進入立法會範圍而被檢控。今天律師通知，控方將申請改控所有涉案人士較重的暴動罪。<br />\n<br />\n原先控方控告我們的罪名為「進入或逗留在會議廳範圍」，最高刑期是監禁三個月；經修改後的控罪最高刑期是監禁十年。<br />\n<br />\n明天我們將會上庭，你會來支持我們嗎？<br />\n<br />\n【七一立會暴動案提堂】<br />\n日期︰6月10日(三)<br />\n時間︰下午2時30分<br />\n地點︰東區裁判法院第一庭"},{"pid":"17f5ccc74ab412f2a67b39122062aec0070bad2a","tid":2056922,"uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T04:40:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dru